better than you give yourself credit for.

59
00:03:15,506 --> 00:03:16,973
I'm sorry.

60
00:03:17,014 --> 00:03:18,975
Um... I think I should go.

61
00:03:19,016 --> 00:03:20,309
- Really?
- Yeah.

62
00:03:20,351 --> 00:03:24,063
But... but... you forgot your shirt!

63
00:03:24,105 --> 00:03:25,856
Keep it.

64
00:03:27,650 --> 00:03:29,610
Though she didn't know it,

65
00:03:29,652 --> 00:03:32,119
