66
00:03:32,154 --> 00:03:36,617
The easiest way to overcome one addiction...

67
00:03:36,659 --> 00:03:40,788
is to replace it with another.

68
00:03:42,189 --> 00:03:44,489
2x18:
Everybody Says Don't

69
00:03:47,528 --> 00:03:49,113
Temptation...

70
00:03:49,155 --> 00:03:51,490
it's the name of a well-known establishment

71
00:03:51,532 --> 00:03:53,743
on the outskirts of Fairview.

72
00:03:53,784 --> 00:03:57,163
Its clientele is devoted.

73
00:03:57,204 --> 00:03:59,623
Everyone who goes there

74
00:03:59,665 --> 00:04:02,510
