92
00:04:45,261 --> 00:04:48,848
and you said that you didn't
want us coming by your house...

93
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:50,892
Thanks, but I'm working, so you gotta go.

94
00:04:50,933 --> 00:04:52,894
Look, we spent a lot of money on that.

95
00:04:52,935 --> 00:04:54,896
The least you can do is open it

96
00:04:54,937 --> 00:04:57,440
so we can bask in your happy expression.

97
00:04:57,481 --> 00:04:58,941
Is there a problem here?

98
00:04:58,983 --> 00:05:01,235
No, we're just talking.
Everything's fine.

99
00:05:01,277 --> 00:05:03,404
Carlos Solis. This is my wife, Gabrielle.

100
00:05:03,446 --> 00:05:04,906
