Didn't I? I thought I had.

104
00:05:14,248 --> 00:05:16,918
What's that, a present for our baby?

105
00:05:18,794 --> 00:05:21,672
I'm sorry, did you just say "our" baby?

106
00:05:21,707 --> 00:05:25,635
Yeah. It's our first.

107
00:05:27,345 --> 00:05:29,430
Hey!

108
00:05:29,472 --> 00:05:30,932
What's for lunch?

109
00:05:30,973 --> 00:05:33,017
Omelettes. You want me to make you one?

110
00:05:33,059 --> 00:05:34,977
