him have his trust fund early

188
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,641
so he could buy a car.

189
00:09:25,682 --> 00:09:28,685
I mean, can you blame me for wanting to know

190
00:09:28,727 --> 00:09:31,271
if I have your support?

191
00:09:31,306 --> 00:09:33,065
And...

192
00:09:33,106 --> 00:09:35,359
so... what,

193
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:38,278
