194
00:09:41,532 --> 00:09:44,243
I actually don't want anything of the sort.

195
00:09:44,284 --> 00:09:47,121
Good.

196
00:09:47,162 --> 00:09:49,123
Because when I give my deposition,

197
00:09:49,164 --> 00:09:51,125
