199
00:10:05,389 --> 00:10:07,391
I want you to look at something.

200
00:10:13,147 --> 00:10:15,656
Myra Holt is talking to Paul Young,

201
00:10:15,691 --> 00:10:18,777
chatting away with him as though
he were any other neighbor.

202
00:10:18,819 --> 00:10:20,779
Now I told her he killed my sister.

203
00:10:20,821 --> 00:10:23,115
I mentioned it to her six
months ago when we were

204
00:10:23,157 --> 00:10:25,117
standing in the express line at the market.

205
00:10:25,159 --> 00:10:27,119
But still, there she is, yakking away.

206
00:10:27,161 --> 00:10:29,253
Oh, Mike.

207
00:10:29,288 --> 00:10:32,291
