210
00:10:37,629 --> 00:10:40,591
if you recall a certain
promise you made to me.

211
00:10:40,632 --> 00:10:44,052
- I am not gonna kill him.
- Why not? Give me one good reason.

212
00:10:44,094 --> 00:10:46,430
