235
00:11:46,532 --> 00:11:49,493
And I sure as hell can't be part of it.

236
00:11:49,535 --> 00:11:50,911
Oh, Mr. Beale, come on.

237
00:11:50,953 --> 00:11:52,663
No, no, hear me out.

238
00:11:52,704 --> 00:11:55,457
If you are determined to
go down this dark road,

239
00:11:55,499 --> 00:11:57,918
and unbeknownst to me steal this...

240
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,212
paternal rights waiver
that's sitting on my desk,

241
00:12:00,254 --> 00:12:03,257
and have this Frank guy sign
both sides and date the top,

242
00:12:03,292 --> 00:12:06,677
I can't be part of that, either.

243
00:12:09,138 --> 00:12:10,264
Hmm.

244
00:12:12,432 --> 00:12:15,853
Okay, I-I'm gonna go to Dad's.

245
00:12:15,894 --> 00:12:18,063
Oh, wait! Why don't you let me walk with you?

246
00:12:18,105 --> 00:12:19,731
Uh, shouldn't you be resting?

247
00:12:19,773 --> 00:12:21,233
